ORDER
PER CURIAM
AND NOW, this 22nd day of October, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Application for an Exercise of Either King’s Bench Powers or Extraordinary Jurisdiction and the Application for Post-Submission Communication are DENIED.
